# Bus Ticket Booking System

## Project Description
The Bus Ticket Booking System is a web-based application developed to allow users to search buses, view schedules, and book tickets online. The system helps manage bus routes, passenger details, and booking records efficiently.

This project demonstrates the use of modern web technologies to build an interactive booking system.

## Features
- Search available buses
- View bus schedules
- Book bus tickets
- Manage passenger information
- Simple and user-friendly interface

## Technologies Used
- React.js
- JavaScript
- HTML
- CSS
- SQL / MySQL

## Tools
- Visual Studio Code
- Node.js
- MySQL
- Git & GitHub

